  "short_description": "\"Journey to Chaos: Pilgrimage to the West\" on Steam! ✨ Pixel-art retelling of Xuanzang’s quest. 📖 20+ story branches—shape heaven’s fate. 🐒 300+ characters, Havoc to 81 trials. ⚔️ Tactics & relics—rebirth = new adventures. 🔥 Wishlist Now!",
