  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎关注微信公众号“抓狗离”</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公众号历史文章会持续更新游戏攻略，可以加入我们的游戏群与其他玩家一起讨论怎么打，以及看到其他我们制作的游戏 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本游戏为西游记故事背景的开放式rpg战棋游<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/b33ba11c9f5fc0c20325921a25fde360.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/b33ba11c9f5fc0c20325921a25fde360.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在随机界面随机出一个角色后开始游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/d0a0ad616d068503b2363b814806b6cc.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/d0a0ad616d068503b2363b814806b6cc.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你觉得合适的技能和较高的五维开始游</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/1071feaa373bd55dab2d692bb4afbffa.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/1071feaa373bd55dab2d692bb4afbffa.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看完简要的游戏说明即可开始游</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/1c77dd9c8f7aabd8643c475168513e47.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/1c77dd9c8f7aabd8643c475168513e47.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进入游戏界面为主基地页面此页面中可跟npc实现各种游戏内的功能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中镶嵌页面是给装备增加一个修为词条如下图所示（注：有该词条的装备需要对应的修为足够才能穿上）（符文可以由战胜对面的挑战npc获得，三级地图的宝箱中也可能开出）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/1d3bfd55909c97834183c0ae8c4f49f2.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/1d3bfd55909c97834183c0ae8c4f49f2.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/ff08cc1de27bb27d1cef33f1afc78a1a.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/ff08cc1de27bb27d1cef33f1afc78a1a.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>挑战副本通过解锁图鉴可以开启（使用系统给的阵容战斗战斗胜利可获得对应的符文）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/509f6a05adf8b73eee3d1af463f70d3c.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/509f6a05adf8b73eee3d1af463f70d3c.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/6541a7768ee65891bf9ac01784e409ef.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/6541a7768ee65891bf9ac01784e409ef.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/cb84f23423c2b645bb44de326143b7ce.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/cb84f23423c2b645bb44de326143b7ce.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>锻造页面可以锻造仓库中的装备，如已经穿在身上需要脱下来。（锻造后穿着的要求会提高，请注意角色的修为是否能够达到穿戴的要求</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/b5c633815504b8c3c24607796400d3e2.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/b5c633815504b8c3c24607796400d3e2.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合页面可以用一个素材和你要提升的角色融合提升角色（满足修为而融合出来的角色不能解锁还没有解锁的图鉴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/33885ec9a9892c60cbd7a59d90428aec.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/33885ec9a9892c60cbd7a59d90428aec.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/33885ec9a9892c60cbd7a59d90428aec.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/33885ec9a9892c60cbd7a59d90428aec.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>融合规则如</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募商店分为仙妖人（只能招募酱油角色作为融合的狗粮）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/c403e97cfa82e9220178e2cb5bbedc01.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/c403e97cfa82e9220178e2cb5bbedc01.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/e19fca4888d6094511a642df9deec1dc.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/e19fca4888d6094511a642df9deec1dc.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/5851bbb7edb51501d851aac55c6f167f.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/5851bbb7edb51501d851aac55c6f167f.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/4cbb5e5abd1c260c40849cc1a656578f.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/4cbb5e5abd1c260c40849cc1a656578f.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>丹药商店需要根据游戏中抉择线路提升的功利点数和金币进行解</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/7f4f98629508422b4a4cbfd28f5e0e56.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/7f4f98629508422b4a4cbfd28f5e0e56.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/5381e382b4de0b1ed9ac60471dd13c1f.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/5381e382b4de0b1ed9ac60471dd13c1f.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>道具商店同理</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/2491ed85b01686594eb1775963d00a1e.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/2491ed85b01686594eb1775963d00a1e.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被动技能商店会根据玩家解锁的图鉴对应解锁</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/2491ed85b01686594eb1775963d00a1e.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/2491ed85b01686594eb1775963d00a1e.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/36169e371b0f242eb23fe940d5f8df59.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/36169e371b0f242eb23fe940d5f8df59.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>主动技能同理<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/80abaf51966c8945e11316bc512d60a4.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/80abaf51966c8945e11316bc512d60a4.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏进程通过完成主线任务解锁（任务会列出该任务需要去什么地图解锁）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/88acb7373e4a27313bb1388cb2b6c828.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/88acb7373e4a27313bb1388cb2b6c828.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>在地图上会有一个特殊的明怪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/45e7e39910ff17733e44e178e00332ee.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/45e7e39910ff17733e44e178e00332ee.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成会解锁下一个任务的战斗以及物资奖励<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/8861b1feedbc03b1145623bce7d35ce9.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/8861b1feedbc03b1145623bce7d35ce9.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中的一些任务可以选择多种后续任务（此任务的选择决定了顶上的三个系数，此三系数影响到后期的遇怪和主基地商店的解锁）<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/3678cf94982c9a5d9e06746f282e315c.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/3678cf94982c9a5d9e06746f282e315c.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇怪规则可以点击顶部的声望说明可以查看</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/ac4f1dc9198ecfa7a2d3e13504b5a516.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/ac4f1dc9198ecfa7a2d3e13504b5a516.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏的底层核心系统是修为系统（修为通过角色升级提高，修为类型可以通过融合增加）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/12fdfad606b89a8051436a07edb49da0.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/12fdfad606b89a8051436a07edb49da0.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/f63f5123945cff95400c8188a5e58f0f.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/f63f5123945cff95400c8188a5e58f0f.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作招募队友有两种方式:1.战斗中使用技能或道具招募;2,酒馆中使用招募券招募</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/d11b25c84653f99370a51f929a0e9e19.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/d11b25c84653f99370a51f929a0e9e19.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一代游戏的五维不设置上限可以通过融合吃药无限提升</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/da4223a461b5193365b3043bf1af4a59.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/da4223a461b5193365b3043bf1af4a59.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伤害计算逻辑如<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/3c2ccdfab722790b129dcac64e6248e4.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/3c2ccdfab722790b129dcac64e6248e4.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此作的技能消耗改成了\"灯\"即角色血条上的黄点<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/f2798c4105d954fbe24c51c5255c4746.avif?t=1747206253\" width=100 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/3f02ed8063a4da6dfafe73ebf97edc0b.avif?t=1747206253\" width=100 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人物前面的那个球中的数字指的是进度条推进速度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此作和封神一致buff只能存在一个用另一个状态就可以覆盖他</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎关注微信公众号“抓狗离”</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公众号历史文章会持续更新游戏攻略，可以加入我们的游戏群与其他玩家一起讨论怎么打，以及看到其他我们制作的游戏 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本游戏为西游记故事背景的开放式rpg战棋游<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/b33ba11c9f5fc0c20325921a25fde360.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/b33ba11c9f5fc0c20325921a25fde360.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在随机界面随机出一个角色后开始游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/d0a0ad616d068503b2363b814806b6cc.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/d0a0ad616d068503b2363b814806b6cc.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你觉得合适的技能和较高的五维开始游</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/1071feaa373bd55dab2d692bb4afbffa.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/1071feaa373bd55dab2d692bb4afbffa.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看完简要的游戏说明即可开始游</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/1c77dd9c8f7aabd8643c475168513e47.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/1c77dd9c8f7aabd8643c475168513e47.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进入游戏界面为主基地页面此页面中可跟npc实现各种游戏内的功能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中镶嵌页面是给装备增加一个修为词条如下图所示（注：有该词条的装备需要对应的修为足够才能穿上）（符文可以由战胜对面的挑战npc获得，三级地图的宝箱中也可能开出）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/1d3bfd55909c97834183c0ae8c4f49f2.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/1d3bfd55909c97834183c0ae8c4f49f2.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/ff08cc1de27bb27d1cef33f1afc78a1a.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/ff08cc1de27bb27d1cef33f1afc78a1a.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>挑战副本通过解锁图鉴可以开启（使用系统给的阵容战斗战斗胜利可获得对应的符文）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/509f6a05adf8b73eee3d1af463f70d3c.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/509f6a05adf8b73eee3d1af463f70d3c.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/6541a7768ee65891bf9ac01784e409ef.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/6541a7768ee65891bf9ac01784e409ef.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/cb84f23423c2b645bb44de326143b7ce.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/cb84f23423c2b645bb44de326143b7ce.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>锻造页面可以锻造仓库中的装备，如已经穿在身上需要脱下来。（锻造后穿着的要求会提高，请注意角色的修为是否能够达到穿戴的要求</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/b5c633815504b8c3c24607796400d3e2.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/b5c633815504b8c3c24607796400d3e2.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合页面可以用一个素材和你要提升的角色融合提升角色（满足修为而融合出来的角色不能解锁还没有解锁的图鉴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/33885ec9a9892c60cbd7a59d90428aec.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/33885ec9a9892c60cbd7a59d90428aec.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/33885ec9a9892c60cbd7a59d90428aec.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/33885ec9a9892c60cbd7a59d90428aec.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>融合规则如</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募商店分为仙妖人（只能招募酱油角色作为融合的狗粮）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/c403e97cfa82e9220178e2cb5bbedc01.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/c403e97cfa82e9220178e2cb5bbedc01.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/e19fca4888d6094511a642df9deec1dc.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/e19fca4888d6094511a642df9deec1dc.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/5851bbb7edb51501d851aac55c6f167f.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/5851bbb7edb51501d851aac55c6f167f.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/4cbb5e5abd1c260c40849cc1a656578f.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/4cbb5e5abd1c260c40849cc1a656578f.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>丹药商店需要根据游戏中抉择线路提升的功利点数和金币进行解</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/7f4f98629508422b4a4cbfd28f5e0e56.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/7f4f98629508422b4a4cbfd28f5e0e56.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/5381e382b4de0b1ed9ac60471dd13c1f.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/5381e382b4de0b1ed9ac60471dd13c1f.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>道具商店同理</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/2491ed85b01686594eb1775963d00a1e.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/2491ed85b01686594eb1775963d00a1e.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被动技能商店会根据玩家解锁的图鉴对应解锁</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/2491ed85b01686594eb1775963d00a1e.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/2491ed85b01686594eb1775963d00a1e.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/36169e371b0f242eb23fe940d5f8df59.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/36169e371b0f242eb23fe940d5f8df59.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>主动技能同理<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/80abaf51966c8945e11316bc512d60a4.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/80abaf51966c8945e11316bc512d60a4.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏进程通过完成主线任务解锁（任务会列出该任务需要去什么地图解锁）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/88acb7373e4a27313bb1388cb2b6c828.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/88acb7373e4a27313bb1388cb2b6c828.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span>在地图上会有一个特殊的明怪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/45e7e39910ff17733e44e178e00332ee.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/45e7e39910ff17733e44e178e00332ee.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成会解锁下一个任务的战斗以及物资奖励<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/8861b1feedbc03b1145623bce7d35ce9.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/8861b1feedbc03b1145623bce7d35ce9.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中的一些任务可以选择多种后续任务（此任务的选择决定了顶上的三个系数，此三系数影响到后期的遇怪和主基地商店的解锁）<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/3678cf94982c9a5d9e06746f282e315c.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/3678cf94982c9a5d9e06746f282e315c.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇怪规则可以点击顶部的声望说明可以查看</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/ac4f1dc9198ecfa7a2d3e13504b5a516.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/ac4f1dc9198ecfa7a2d3e13504b5a516.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏的底层核心系统是修为系统（修为通过角色升级提高，修为类型可以通过融合增加）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/12fdfad606b89a8051436a07edb49da0.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/12fdfad606b89a8051436a07edb49da0.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/f63f5123945cff95400c8188a5e58f0f.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/f63f5123945cff95400c8188a5e58f0f.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作招募队友有两种方式:1.战斗中使用技能或道具招募;2,酒馆中使用招募券招募</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/d11b25c84653f99370a51f929a0e9e19.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/d11b25c84653f99370a51f929a0e9e19.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一代游戏的五维不设置上限可以通过融合吃药无限提升</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/da4223a461b5193365b3043bf1af4a59.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/da4223a461b5193365b3043bf1af4a59.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伤害计算逻辑如<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/3c2ccdfab722790b129dcac64e6248e4.avif?t=1747206253\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras_big/3c2ccdfab722790b129dcac64e6248e4.avif?t=1747206253 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此作的技能消耗改成了\"灯\"即角色血条上的黄点<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/f2798c4105d954fbe24c51c5255c4746.avif?t=1747206253\" width=100 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3678920/extras/3f02ed8063a4da6dfafe73ebf97edc0b.avif?t=1747206253\" width=100 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人物前面的那个球中的数字指的是进度条推进速度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此作和封神一致buff只能存在一个用另一个状态就可以覆盖他</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
